{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn about the mysteries of Trifoil by exploring and solving line drawing puzzles. In Trifoil the line always interacts with itself, in this rules discovery open world logic puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/extras/custom_image_tjunction.png?t=1736855922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Trifoil will have over 200 hand-crafted puzzles designed to slowly expose the players to the puzzle rules, flip them on their head then introduce new ones. If you like thinky games, rule-discovery and twists this is for you.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/extras/custom_screenshot_puzzle_fail.png?t=1736855922\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A demo will be available for Steam Nextfest February 2025. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While waiting for the demo join the discord (link on the right) and become a play tester!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Trifoil music was composed by Grzegorz Bednorz.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736855922","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736855922","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/0a767cc61c3ec3e637d96417ba315cddf1b9d06a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736855922","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/0a767cc61c3ec3e637d96417ba315cddf1b9d06a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736855922","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"con